                  </persName>
            . I was sitting at brekafast behind the the shop on the morning in question, and I saw a hand reach something off the cutting board in the shop. I immediately jumped up, and missed the shoes in question from the cutting board.</p>

               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18161030-71-person619">
