                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18161030-71-off349 t18161030-71-crimeloc351"></join>. The prisoner was one, and I saw him reach into the shop, and take the shoes, and I followed him as far as Manchester-street, where I stopped him with the shoes in his possession, and brought him back.</p>
